firstTrue-preserves-allFalse Оұ allF (suc n) with Оұ zero | allF zero
... | true  | Оұ0=f = ex-falso (falseвүўtrue (sym Оұ0=f))
... | false | _    = firstTrue-preserves-allFalse (Оұ вҲҳ suc) (allF вҲҳ suc) n

