firstTrue-true-implies-original-true Оұ (suc n) ft-sn=t with Оұ zero
... | true  = ex-falso (falseвүўtrue ft-sn=t)
... | false = firstTrue-true-implies-original-true (Оұ вҲҳ suc) n ft-sn=t

