interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition : (t : freeBATerms в„•) вҶ’ interpretBвҲһ t вүЎ ПҖвҲһ-from-terms t
interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition (Tvar n) =
  gвҲһ n
    вүЎвҹЁ cong (fst ПҖвҲһ) (sym (includeBATerms-Tvar n)) вҹ©
  ПҖвҲһ-from-terms (Tvar n) вҲҺ
interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition (Tconst false) =
  рқҹҳвҲһ
    вүЎвҹЁ sym ПҖвҲһ-0 вҹ©
  fst ПҖвҲһ (BooleanRingStr.рқҹҳ (snd (freeBA в„•)))
    вүЎвҹЁ cong (fst ПҖвҲһ) (sym includeBATerms-0) вҹ©
  ПҖвҲһ-from-terms (Tconst false) вҲҺ
interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition (Tconst true) =
  рқҹҷвҲһ
    вүЎвҹЁ sym ПҖвҲһ-1 вҹ©
  fst ПҖвҲһ (BooleanRingStr.рқҹҷ (snd (freeBA в„•)))
    вүЎвҹЁ cong (fst ПҖвҲһ) (sym includeBATerms-1) вҹ©
  ПҖвҲһ-from-terms (Tconst true) вҲҺ
interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition (t +T s) =
  interpretBвҲһ t +вҲһ interpretBвҲһ s
    вүЎвҹЁ congвӮӮ _+вҲһ_ (interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition t) (interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition s) вҹ©
  ПҖвҲһ-from-terms t +вҲһ ПҖвҲһ-from-terms s
    вүЎвҹЁ sym (ПҖвҲһ-+ (fst includeBATermsSurj t) (fst includeBATermsSurj s)) вҹ©
  fst ПҖвҲһ (BooleanRingStr._+_ (snd (freeBA в„•)) (fst includeBATermsSurj t) (fst includeBATermsSurj s))
    вүЎвҹЁ cong (fst ПҖвҲһ) (sym (includeBATerms-+ t s)) вҹ©
  ПҖвҲһ-from-terms (t +T s) вҲҺ
interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition (-T t) =
  interpretBвҲһ t
    вүЎвҹЁ interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition t вҹ©
  ПҖвҲһ-from-terms t
    вүЎвҹЁ cong (fst ПҖвҲһ) (BooleanAlgebraStr.-IsId (freeBA в„•) {x = fst includeBATermsSurj t}) вҹ©
  fst ПҖвҲһ (BooleanRingStr.-_ (snd (freeBA в„•)) (fst includeBATermsSurj t))
    вүЎвҹЁ cong (fst ПҖвҲһ) (sym (includeBATerms-- t)) вҹ©
  ПҖвҲһ-from-terms (-T t) вҲҺ
interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition (t В·T s) =
  interpretBвҲһ t В·вҲһ interpretBвҲһ s
    вүЎвҹЁ congвӮӮ _В·вҲһ_ (interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition t) (interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition s) вҹ©
  ПҖвҲһ-from-terms t В·вҲһ ПҖвҲһ-from-terms s
    вүЎвҹЁ sym (ПҖвҲһ-В· (fst includeBATermsSurj t) (fst includeBATermsSurj s)) вҹ©
  fst ПҖвҲһ (BooleanRingStr._В·_ (snd (freeBA в„•)) (fst includeBATermsSurj t) (fst includeBATermsSurj s))
    вүЎвҹЁ cong (fst ПҖвҲһ) (sym (includeBATerms-В· t s)) вҹ©
  ПҖвҲһ-from-terms (t В·T s) вҲҺ

interpretBвҲһ-surjective : isSurjection interpretBвҲһ
interpretBвҲһ-surjective x =
  PT.map (О» { (t , eq) вҶ’ t , interpretBвҲһ-eq-composition t вҲҷ eq }) (ПҖвҲһ-includeTerms-surj x)

