xor-nf : BвҲһ-NormalForm вҶ’ BвҲһ-NormalForm вҶ’ BвҲһ-NormalForm
xor-nf (joinForm ns) (joinForm ms) = joinForm (ns в–іL ms)
xor-nf (joinForm ns) (meetNegForm ms) = meetNegForm (ns в–іL ms)
xor-nf (meetNegForm ns) (joinForm ms) = meetNegForm (ms в–іL ns)
xor-nf (meetNegForm ns) (meetNegForm ms) = joinForm (ns в–іL ms)

meet-nf : BвҲһ-NormalForm вҶ’ BвҲһ-NormalForm вҶ’ BвҲһ-NormalForm
meet-nf (joinForm ns) (joinForm ms) = joinForm (ns вҲ©L ms)
meet-nf (joinForm ns) (meetNegForm ms) = joinForm (ns вҲ–L ms)
meet-nf (meetNegForm ns) (joinForm ms) = joinForm (ms вҲ–L ns)
meet-nf (meetNegForm ns) (meetNegForm ms) = meetNegForm (ns ++ ms)

normalizeTerm : freeBATerms в„• вҶ’ BвҲһ-NormalForm
normalizeTerm (Tvar n) = joinForm (n вҲ· [])
normalizeTerm (Tconst false) = joinForm []
normalizeTerm (Tconst true) = meetNegForm []
normalizeTerm (t +T s) = xor-nf (normalizeTerm t) (normalizeTerm s)
normalizeTerm (-T t) = normalizeTerm t
normalizeTerm (t В·T s) = meet-nf (normalizeTerm t) (normalizeTerm s)

