      вүЎвҹЁ congвӮӮ _+Г—_
           (IsCommRingHom.presВ· (snd ПҶQ) eQ (fst ПҲL a))
           (IsCommRingHom.presВ· (snd ПҶQ) eQ' (fst ПҲR b)) вҹ©
